event.title: AP Inter Results
event.description:
The Andhra pradhesh Intermediate Results will be declared on May 2018 onwards .The AP Inter
results will be announced by the Board of Intermediate Education of Andhra pradhesh (BIEAP) and the
board was conducted the Intermediate exams for academic 2017-2018 year in various examination
centers across the Andhra pradhesh state.
